Lyrics :- 
Sath Pheron Se Bandha
Janmo Ka Ye Bandhan
Pyar Se Joda Hai Rabb Ne
Preet Ka Daman 
Hai Nayi Rasme, Nayi Kasame
Nayi Uljhan
Hont Hai Khamosh
Lekin Keh Rahi Dhakan

Tere naam ke harf ki tasbeeh ko, saanson
Ke gale ka haar kiya, duniya bhooli aur sirf
tujhe haan sirf tujhe hi pyar kiya

Tum jeet gaye hum hare, 
Tum jeet gaye hum hare, hum hare aur tum jeete
Mere dil ki dil se tauba, dil se tauba mere Dil ki
Dil ki tauba hai dil ab pyar dobara na hoga

Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol o yaara o yaara
Bol kaffara kya hoga

Humne dhadkan dhadkan karke,
dil tere dil se jod liya
Ankhon ne ankhen padh padh ke, 
tujhe vird bana ke yaad kiya

Tujhe pyaar kiya toh tu hi bata, hum ne kya koi jurm kiya
Or jurm kiya hai toh bhi bata, ye jurm ki jurm ki kya hai sazaa

Tumhe hum se badh kar duniya, duniya tumhe humse badhkar
Dil galti kar baitha hai,galti kar baitha hai dil
Haaye dil galti kar baitha tu bol kaffara kya hoga

Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol o yaara o yaara
Bol kaffara kya hoga

Dhadkan meri dhadkan
Dhadkan meri dhadkan
Dhadkan ‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶

snippet.description:

Adding to the fire of ‚ÄòSunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari‚Äô, Guru Randhawa joins the party with PERFECT! üî• Composed and written by Guru Randhawa, Rony Ajnali and Gill Machhrai, the song is sung by Guru Randhawa. Lyrics:

Sir to pairan de takk
You r so perfect
Pind to shehran de takk
You r so perfect

Kim to v gol lakk
Because You r so perfect
Saare te Tere te jatonde hakk
Because You r so perfect

Sohniye bullan di teri surkhi
Tu patt dita turki
Gall teri turpi

Haye Heer ne a diti tenu gudti
Ni fit Teri kurti
Lata di jiwe murki

Agg lone nakhre ne Patt ta punjab ni
Tuhi kalli dunia te kutt di swaad ni
Tere aage lagde husan saare farzi
Na koi tetho pehla sohni na koi tetho baad ni

Gol gol addian di thakk thakk
You r so perfect
Dressa utte laawe lakh
You r so perfect

Matthe ali teri latt
You r so perfect
Teri juye to v maadi latt
Not so Perfect

Lembo vangu vish vish dharti te ture
Tera Dubbel swing lakk khaye ni
London de sab to mashoor darji to
Gale paan patte ale tu rakaye ni

Akhian to shed shed chakk di nai
Lang jawe Mundyea nu takk di nai
Kade LA kade tu dubai huni ae
Kr kr shoppinga tu thakk di nai

Kacrch di lakh lakh
You r so perfect
Nikl di jach jach
You r so perfect
Teri beauty nu number 10
You r so perfect
Chobaran nu pondi gash
No so perfect

Husna da dang maare Naag di bachi
Toba toba agg kudi banke nachi
Naina ch saroor 7 bottela jinna
Reshami jehe aang odi Umar kachi

Guru nu v maare akh
You r so perfect
Gill Rony laye patt
You r so perfect
Pinda de tu maare jatt
You r so perfect
Tenu maaf ne Qatal 8
Not so perfect

snippet.title: Wakka Lagdo Sansar - bekcha - Jodi No.1 Title Song [Lyrical Video]
snippet.description:
#wakkalagdosansar #Jodino1 #bekcha 
Wakka Lagdo Sansar is the original soundtrack for an amazing web series Jodi No. 1 made with love, soul and perseverance by brilliant human beings with big dreams. When you have the time and mind, go catch it here:

The first episode: https://youtu.be/lCakw0IyOt4
Full Channel : https://www.youtube.com/@UC3uDjw2Sg4EgPfZeAR_Q2rQ 

I would like to pay respects to the brave fighters, martyrs of the current movement in Nepal. The whole nation mourns this massive loss and is forever indebted to all of  you.  I am sending out prayers to the bereaved family and friends.

I sit here many miles away wondering what went wrong, why this had to happen and if the unbearable losses had to happen. I fail to make sense of most of it. There is but a glimmer of hope with this morning's announcement. But I still have fear in the back of my mind that things may turn out worse. I hope I am wrong and I hope better days are on the way. Thank you,  Generation Z, all the mighty warriors from September 8, everyone who took part in this revolution. 


Also, I'm not sure right now is a space for me to describe the song. To put it briefly, this expresses frustration and annoyance at how at times the endless torment life can feel like. If this makes you feel worse, maybe come back to the song some other time. The release was planned a week back,  and things went seriously south, but maybe now we shall all slowly resume. Shall come back with more... The official video will be out soon.

Wishing all of you strength, peace and love. Please keep up the kindness, camaraderie and  the big little things. I hope to be able to help in some way.

Audio Credits:
(Produced, Mixed and Mastered by) https://www.instagram.com/begendra_official
https://www.instagram.com/anmolz_music
Guitars: https://www.instagram.com/bishalchhetriguitar/
Sansic Productions

i'm in instagram sometimes - https://www.instagram.com/b3kcha
and mail me here, if you feel it should get to me: songsbybekcha@gmail.com
